OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1772565072
OL,3,CHistoric pub brought back to life at
OL,4,CCarlisle Railway Station
OL,6,FA pub reputed to have been frequented
OL,7,Fby Queen Victoria has reopened at
OL,8,FCarlisle's railway station.
OL,10,FThe Scott & Brassey pub on platform 4
OL,11,Fhas welcomed its first customers after
OL,12,Fa #400,000 renovation.
OL,14,FIndependent pub chain Lancaster
OL,15,FBrewery say that they have tired to
OL,16,Fsympathetically bring back to life the
OL,17,Fatmosphere of the 19th century when it
OL,18,Fis said Queen Victoria visited during
OL,19,Ftrips to Carlisle.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/5
