PN,35902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1772565072
OL,3,CHistoric pub brought back to life at
OL,4,CCarlisle Railway Station
OL,6,FIt is part of the #27million council-
OL,7,Fled Station Gateway Project, that is
OL,8,Fin the process of transforming the
OL,9,Farea around Carlisle Railway station
OL,10,Fin order to attract more visitors to
OL,11,Fthe city.
OL,13,FThe name of the pub is taken from Sir
OL,14,FWalter Scott, the 19th century author
OL,15,Fof historical novels who set many of
OL,16,Fhis stories in Carlisle and got
OL,17,Fmarried at the city's cathedral, and
OL,18,FThomas Brassey, one of the great
OL,19,FVictorian railway builders who oversaw
OL,20,Fconstruction of the Lancaster and
OL,21,FCarlisle railway in the 1840s.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/5
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,360,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1772565072
OL,3,CHistoric pub brought back to life at
OL,4,CCarlisle Railway Station
OL,6,FBosses at Lancaster Brewery who will
OL,7,Frun the pub say they hope to attract
OL,8,Fnot just passengers using the railway
OL,9,Fbut also serve people on a night out
OL,10,Fin Carlisle.
OL,12,FSpeaking to ITV Border Phil Simpson,
OL,13,FManaging Director at Lancaster Brewery
OL,14,Fsaid: "We own quite a few pubs that
OL,15,Fare in listed buildings, and we've
OL,16,Falways liked that sort of combination
OL,17,Fof historical and modern.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/5
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,360,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1772565072
OL,3,CHistoric pub brought back to life at
OL,4,CCarlisle Railway Station
OL,6,F"We have a pub in Lancaster station,
OL,7,Fwhich is the prototype and has done
OL,8,Freally well, and we're very happy with
OL,9,Fme. We wanted to replicate that. So
OL,10,Fwhen this became available, this
OL,11,Fseemed like a logical step."
OL,13,FWhile Kerry Riley, Customer Experience
OL,14,FDirector at Avanti West Coast, added:
OL,15,F"This is the first step within a wider
OL,16,Fregeneration of the station area at
OL,17,FCarlisle.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/5
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
