OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,360,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1772565072
OL,3,CHistoric pub brought back to life at
OL,4,CCarlisle Railway Station
OL,6,F"There's an awful lot of planning and
OL,7,Fwork to come in the pedestrianised
OL,8,Fareas outside of the station and the
OL,9,Fcustomer floor for customers coming
OL,10,Fthrough the Carlisle."
OL,12,FThe pub, which doesn't plan to serve
OL,13,Ffood, had been used as a waiting room
OL,14,Fwith a cafe for a number of decades
OL,15,Fbut had been empty until it was
OL,16,Fdecided to renovate it to a drinking
OL,17,Festablishment.
OL,19,FIt will be open until 10 pm during the
OL,20,Fweek with a closing time of 11pm on
OL,21,FFriday and Saturday nights.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/5
